summary: Adds a player room to Tel Mithryn and lots of magical clutter. "Neloth your giant mushroom is no longer a messy man cave" Also adds a alchemy bench, tanning rack and anvil inside the main tower. The aim is to make Tel Mithryn feel more magical and a place to call home :)
descriptionHtml:
[size=5][center][color=#6d9eeb][b]Tel Mithryn Magical Clutter
[/b][/color][/center][/size][color=#93c47d]This mod adds a player room to Tel Mithryn and lots of magical clutter. Neloth's giant mushroom is no longer a messy man cave. Also adds a alchemy bench, tanning rack and anvil inside the main tower. The aim is to make Tel Mithryn feel more magical and a place to call home!

[/color][center][color=#f6b26b]I really love this DLC and I hope you can enjoy this small mod![/color][/center]
